snippet.title: Dungeon Kingdom: Sign of the Moon Early Access Trailer
snippet.description:
Here is the latest trailer for "Dungeon Kingdom: Sign of the Moon" soon to be in Early Access on Steam! Play the game as soon as it's released by purchasing the game on Steam:
http://store.steampowered.com/app/329040/

Or from the Dungeon Kingdom website:
http://www.Dungeon-Kingdom.com
